---
title: Steak Sandwiches with Horseradish Cream & Tomato-Watercress Salad
description: There's nothing like slices of juicy steak in a crusty ciabatta sandwich. Tangy horseradish cream is a classic condiment, and sweet red onions, perfectly bitter watercress, and roasted tomatoes really round out this take on a steakhouse dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5512a9966ced6e37098b4569.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/5512a9966ced6e37098b4569.pdf
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
